title: Marvel Crisis Protocol: Crystal and Lockjaw
description: A princess of the Inhuman royal family and the teleporting bulldog who serves as the family's protector join your epic tabletop miniatures battles! Features two unpainted, unassembled miniatures and everything you'll need to deploy them.
